		"Id": "chassisdef_lament_LMT-AEF",
		"Name": "Acta Est Fabula",
		"Details": "Owned and operated by a Canopian noble named Melie Larkell, Acta Est Fabula is a blunt instrument meant to drive for victory in the best way possible: a straight line. Larkell might have been too aggressive for the business world, the acting stage, and even for the military, but that level of raw aggression and dedication to victory served her very well in the arenas of Solaris VII where Acta Est Fabula has been quite a hit. While it is armed with twin Snub-Nose PPCs and an exotic ER Medium Laser variant, the design is truly built around charging right into opponents with a TSM-enhanced Lance in the right arm. The weapons are secondary to the Lance hits and when the Lance hits, victory isn't far behind. Given Larkell's record in the arenas, it seems she might just be onto something.",
